</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class='talk-speakers'>
<div class='talk-speaker media'>
<a class='talk-speaker__image media__image media__image--thumb' href='/speakers/eric_liu'>
<span class="thumb thumb--square"><span class="thumb__sizer"><span class="thumb__tugger"><img alt="" class=" thumb__image" play="false" src="http://img.tedcdn.com/r/images.ted.com/images/ted/279f4e597613f1e651cae453a0fccf6b8ef8c578_254x191.jpg?" /><span class="thumb__aligner"></span></span></span></span>
</a>
<div class='talk-speaker__details media__message'>
<div class='talk-speaker__name h10'>
<a class="l3 talk-speaker__link" href="/speakers/eric_liu">Eric Liu</a>
</div>
<div class='talk-speaker__description'>
Civics educator
</div>
<div class='talk-speaker__bio'>
Eric Liu is a civics educator and founder of Citizen University, which brings together leaders, activists and practitioners to teach the art of effective and creative citizenship.
<a class="l3 talk-speaker__link" href="/speakers/eric_liu">Full bio</a>
</div>
</div>
